Package com.service.kerberos.rest.client

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IKerberosAuthenticationClient
    This interface provides the functionality of Kerberos Authentication for the Application.
    IKerberosKeyServerClient
    This interface provides the functionality to securely connect with Key Server to get Secret Keys
    IKerberosServiceTicketClient
    This interface allows to get the ServiceTicket from the Kerberos Server for the service to be invoked by the Application
